// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0428 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 854e3bc9-1213-5f40-aa84-631a841eff84

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:2.0*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
